
// Things to do after installing Raspian Wheezy
// HPH Knowledgebase
// Fluvio L. Lobo Fenoglietto

1- Install the LibreOffice suite:

1.1- Libre Writer -- sudo apt-get install libreoffice-writer
1.2- Libre Spreadsheet -- sudo apt-get install libreoffice-calc
1.3- Libre Presentation -- sudo apt-get install libreoffice-impress
1.4- Libre Drawing -- sudo apt-get install libreoffice-draw
1.5- Libre Database -- sudo apt-get install libreoffice-base
1.6- Libre Equation Editor -- sudo apt-get install libreoffice-math
1.7- Libre Mobile Devices Filter -- sudo apt-get install libreoffice-filter-mobiledev

2- Install Virtual Keyboard for touchscreen applications

2.1- Matchbox Keyboard -- sudo apt-get install matchbox-keyboard
2.2- Create desktop shortcut to execute virtual keyboard (see guide)